survey_response.review_text: Dr. Ajay Rao is a very competent and kind doctor. During my first consultation, he patiently asked several questions to understand the background and thoughtly analyzed the issue. He was not rushed in his physical check of the knee. He then took the time to summarize his root cause hypothesis, describe the next steps and provide recommendations on proper care & exercise. Through my two visits, he was unfailingly courteous and his course of action helped me get over my knee issues. Highly recommend Dr. Rao.

After Diagnosis doctor has suggested 3 types exercise and prescribed medicine and my father relaxed and very happy with treatment given by Dr. Ajay Rao.
